Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't we kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This girl who teases me, saying as such...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait... who is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MAY 29th
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"What is written hereafter is\Ntruly something unbelievable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is the truth,\Nso make sure to read until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have to!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}It was my senpai, a third-year\Nat Minegahara High School.\NI went to Fujisawa Library, and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"May 6th. I met a wild bunny girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:26.87,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#1 - My Senpai is a Bunny Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MAY 6th
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.\NSo, you can still see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're Sakurajima-senpai, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're calling me "senpai",\Nit means you go to Minegahara High School?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakuta Azusagawa, class 2-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa is spelled like the Azusagawa Rest Area,\Nand Sakuta is spelled "blooming Taro".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mai Sakurajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurajima is spelled like Mai Sakurajima,\Nand Mai is spelled like Mai Sakurajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. You're a celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about what you saw today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't have anything to do with me\Nunder any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, then say "yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She told me to forget, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, it's morning. Wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, it's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Half of Kaede is made of her feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that embarrassing setup?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're already at a decent age,\Nmaybe outgrow crawling into my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, because you wake up too excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd get excited over their little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.85,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you like bunny girls, Kunimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you love them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, I love them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For example, if you were to bump into\Na pretty bunny girl at the library,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd do a double-take.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'd totally gawk at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KANAGAWA PREFECTURAL\NMINEGAHARA HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kunimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can see Sakurajima-senpai, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, crystal clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what kind of a person she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Well, she's a celebrity, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's still in showbiz,\Neven though she's on hiatus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I was surprised to discover\Nthat she attends our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to see you show interest\Nin a girl other than Shoko Makinohara,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she's probably impossible, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to ask her out,\Nlet alone be in love with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just thinking how I've never seen her\Ntogether with someone else at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's always alone, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Yuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kamisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Sakuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from a senpai on my team...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently Sakurajima didn't come to school\Nat the start of her first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She declared going on hiatus\Nstraight out of middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she was locked into some prior titles,\Nso she apparently was busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said she didn't seriously go to school\Nuntil after summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sakurajima-senpai, the celebrity who\Nstarted school midway through the first year,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is totally an outsider.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once the class takes its shape,\Nit doesn't change easily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Others will talk behind your back if you stand out,\Ncalling you annoying or a show off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And once that happens, everyone knows\Nthat there's no going back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the kind of pace a school is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody can approach\NSakurajima-senpai to talk to her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They don't want to stand out,\Nto be isolated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why Sakurajima-senpai\Nis also reading the situation,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and pretending to act accordingly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be blunt.\NDon't talk to Yuuma ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'm interfering\Nin Kunimi's relationship with you, Kamisato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows about\Nthe Hospitalization Incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that Hospitalization Incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuuma hangs out with the class loner,\Nhis popularity will plummet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel sorry for him if that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So by that logic, your own popularity\Nis taking a nosedive, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you're fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just accepting your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so irritated?\NAre you on your period?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die, idiot! Just die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This just can't be! You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the end...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone says "I'm bored" or "Isn't there\Nanything interesting out there?" like pet phrases.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But in reality, none of them are\Nreally looking for a change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's gotta be Mai Sakurajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's totally her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a pic just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, look this way a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.66,0:08:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A human. What are you,\Nan ogling photographer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wha— Why, you..!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy?\NLike it's anything much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You thought I'd get mad\Nand say to mind your own business?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it, but I'm holding it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I wish you didn't say that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it wears you down inside, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wears down...\NYou're right about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Incoming call - Manager"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The train is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I know what that woman wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About that thing yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you to forget about it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bunny outfit was so erotic,\Nit's impossible to forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on! You didn't do anything weird\Nwhile thinking about me, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm totally fine with being the subject\Nof erotic fantasies for young boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Azusagawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the rumors about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Minegahara High School homepage\NHigh Schools in Kanagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something about a violent incident where\Nyou sent three classmates to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}1) Sakuta Azusagawa - dude sent 3 classmates\Nto the hospital after a violent incident in middle school.\NHe moved outta Yokohama - where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}2) What's this hospitalization incident?\N3) so scary lolol....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored that you'd take an interest in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this information about one individual\Nbeing out in the open like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was written\Nto this extent, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look it up yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a smartphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to, but I got frustrated\Nand tossed it into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throw trash away into trash cans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any friends, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends? I have two, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you say "even" with just two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel having two friends\Nis more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to be friends with them\Nfor the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did you think about\Nthe Hospitalization Incident rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty clear after some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who caused such a huge incident\Ncouldn't attend school like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.31,0:11:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish my class could hear that line.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it's wrong, then you need to tell them such.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A rumor is kind of like\Nthe atmosphere, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since lately, the atmosphere\Nis something you need to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That "atmosphere" that labels you as\Na bad person if you can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the people creating that atmosphere\Ndon't have a sense of participation,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it's foolish to try\Nand fight against the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're leaving misunderstandings be,\Nand giving up before even fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn to talk, Senpai.\NWhat was all that about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made my debut when I was six years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After getting the lead role\Nfor the morning drama series,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,television, movies, commercials...\NI was always in the public eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't a day where I didn't\Nsee Mai Sakurajima on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun in the beginning,\Nbut it gradually became more stressful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People would notice and say,\N"That's THE Mai Sakurajima!" everywhere I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And at some point, I started wishing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that I could go to a world\Nwhere nobody knew who I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I first noticed that people weren't able\Nto see me at the beginning of a 4-day weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On a whim, I went to the aquarium.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and that's what she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh? You're kidding me!\N- It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was just me at first,\Nsince they were focused on viewing the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I stopped in a café\Non my way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a shop that you did something\Nso terrible they banned your patronage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.73,0:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, your foot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong with my foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm ecstatic that you\Nare stomping on mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, quickly left the café\Nand went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But after returning to Fujisawa,\Neveryone saw me normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I went around, seeing if something\Nsimilar would happen in other places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were a bunny girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking like this, people would stare\Nif they saw me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going out as\Na wild bunny girl again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right, so don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One custard bun, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, one custard bun, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. A custard-filled bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you at all troubled by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Not being able to eat\Nthe custard-filled buns here is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But do you actually believe\Nthis insane story of mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know what stories like that are called.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Adolescence Syndrome," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Adolescence Syndrome, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing other people's thoughts,\Nor seeing another person's future,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or swapping bodies with someone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rumors of that nature\Nstarted being called Adolescence Syndrome,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,though nobody knows who coined the term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's just an urban legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to show you\Nso you'll believe me when I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I believe you."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You keep it rather clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Senpai, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop with that "Senpai" thing.\NI don't recall ever becoming your senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurajima-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My last name is a bit long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember to add the "-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Mai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't come across as "Azusagawa,"\Nso I'll call you "Sakuta-kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you stripping!?\NYou said you weren't going to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy! Perverted! Exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's real, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think there are idiots\Nwho'd wear special make-up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.78,0:16:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any weird noises!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit sensitive there, so please be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.79,0:16:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That feels really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Pain! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just seem to be enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what caused such a wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not really sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My little sister Kaede.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't assaulted or anything.\NJust bullied on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what you're trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.60,0:16:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something about not replying\Nto a message...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A girl who was the leader\Nof her class started hating her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and people wrote all sorts of insults\Nin social media groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}DIE KAEDE
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:16:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I believe\NAdolescence Syndrome really exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That wound is from back then, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea how or why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I awoke one morning covered in blood,\Nand was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the truth\Nbehind the Hospitalization Incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was the one sent to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S-So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going to call for a professional lady\Ndelivered to you, please say so in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kaede, you're making\Na big misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is she making you buy a vase?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What about English-learning supplies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't even recommended one,\Nso rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's a senpai from my school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mai Sakurajima. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Kaede Azusagawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, she said, "Nice to meet you.\NI'm Kaede Azusagawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Nasuno.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"And this is Nasuno," she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting me know, Kaede-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NShe's very afraid of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays she loves the house so much,\Nshe doesn't even go to school anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So she doesn't know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...\NShe doesn't watch much TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}For Kaede, distancing herself from the internet\Nsubsided symptoms of Adolescence Syndrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hence why I threw my smartphone\Ninto the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}So you're saying my case\Nbares similarity to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I mean, you're reacting\Nto the atmosphere at school perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So to avoid making the situation any worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.36,0:19:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's better for you\Nto return to show business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you stand out a lot on TV,\Neveryone else won't leave you alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,even if you play\Nthe role of the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you seem to want\Nto return to show-biz yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you had a disapproving look\Ntowards the movie ad on the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have skill and experience,\Neven a manager who eagerly awaits your—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, the bathroom is—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since then, Mai-san hasn't shown up to school.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I seem to have stepped on\Na huge landmine or such.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Mai Sakurajima hiatus reason [search]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Touched a part of Mai-san\NI wasn't supposed to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Related words: Mai Sakurajima pregnant / mother\Nsleeping up the ladder / wrist-cut wounds\Nfleeing overseas / porn / schoolgirl prostitution
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kunimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Mai Sakurajima\Nsaid she was going on hiatus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.28,0:20:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it to focus on studying,\Nor at least superficially?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Azusagawa, that female announcer\Nis here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And who were you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that's how you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}BKS Television - Announcer Division\NFumika Nanjo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And what can I do for you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the area\Ncovering a story about young sardines.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I had the afternoon off,\NI came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One Sakuta-kun to-go, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be out of your mind,\Nso I'll assume your order is one ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't bring yourself\Nto talk about the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just need one picture\Nof the scar on your chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nanjo-san, would you know the reason\Nwhy Mai Sakurajima went on hiatus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know things normal folks don't,\Nto say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're head-over-heels\Nfor Sakurajima-senpai lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you've gotten over\NShoko Makinohara, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First Kunimi, now you...\NWhy do you guys make that connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Add sugar if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is safe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably sugar inside.\NI mean, it's white.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what did you want to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Futaba, do you think it's possible\Nto lose sight of someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about your vision,\Ngo see an optometrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:22:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As in someone is there but you\Ncan't see them, like the invisible man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to sneak into\Nthe girls' bathroom or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Azusagawa.\NSuch a rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not into scat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're referring to Adolescence Syndrome,\NI believe I've already said it before,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I stand in the denial camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.10,0:22:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's just unreasonable.\NSo I came here for a reasonable explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, I'm sitting right\Nin front of you, Futaba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it logically possible for me\Nto become invisible to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd need to be engrossed in something,\Nor simply space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The human brain doesn't look at\Nthe things it doesn't want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.58,0:22:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.\NBut if it isn't something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's also the measurement theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Measurement theory?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The theory that the existence of something\Nis confirmed only when it is observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you've at least heard\Nabout the cat in the box, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.10,0:22:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Schrödinger's Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Sakurajima existed while in show-biz,\Nwhen everyone could see her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have one custard bun, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.62,0:23:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one custard bun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you know who Mai Sakurajima is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the child actor Mai Sakurajima,\Nwho got her break in that morning drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.55,0:23:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sakurajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.46,0:23:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was there someone by that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.39,0:23:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fact that people no longer see her\Nmeans not only that people cannot see her...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, her existence in itself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to see me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm starving."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.42,0:24:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your personality sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.97,0:24:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.18,0:24:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did you change into\Na hungry-girl type, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't buy anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For two weeks, more and more people\Nhave become unable to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere around Fujisawa Station\Nis no good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.15,0:24:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, here.\NWant to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.41,0:24:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"May 6th. I met a wild bunny girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.96,0:24:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was the beginning. This is how we met.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way I can forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.38,0:24:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must remember, even if you forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.67,0:24:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be sure to do a good job, future me."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.93,0:24:58.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing less from you, Azusagawa.\NSuch a rascal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.97,0:24:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time\N#2 On First Dates, Trouble is Essential
